node.text:
We shot this entire collection in Mexico and it was an incredible experience. The culture was heavily present at @lasalamandasmexico in the architecture, food, and people. It was unforgettable for my whole family and I’m forever grateful to @fashiontofigure for making it happen and hiring locals to assist on the shoot. 

And if it wasn’t for all of your support, that little girl running around the streets of Guadalajara 20 years ago, would’ve never seen the success she has seen today. Thank you guys SO much y ¡Viva México! 🇲🇽 

#SRVxFTF
